pyNotes
=================

1. install dependendies with pip install -r requirements.txt
2. pywin32 may need this: python -m pywin32_postinstall
3. run either with the shell script or with the py launcher on windows

note that on windows you'll need to install dejavusansmono ttf font to print
also note that the windows version is worse (to be expected)

